         butterInputTitle: "<i class='fa-solid fa-vial-circle-check'></i> Experiment Setup: The Butter Constant", butterInputDesc: "Alright, Scientist! First things first. How much of that glorious unsalted butter üßà are we dedicating to science today? Punch in the deets below. No skimping!", butterLabel: 'Butter Amount', grams: 'grams', cups: 'cups', butterWarningMsg: "Hold up! ‚úã Need at least 100g (~1/2 cup) butter for valid results!", butterButton: "Calibrate & Proceed! <i class='fas fa-arrow-right'></i>",
